## React Introduction : So react is just a javascript library given to the js developers to use by the facebook meta engineers it is the prewritten code written by meta engineers and react is just a object.And in the index.js files i have also explained why we need react how things used to happens before react and what are the issues we used to face everything so now we are done with react introduction.

## When we have React why do we need ReactDOM->So react is a library indepandant and it is not only used in web it is also used in builduiing mobile applications so React ke through hum elements bana skte hai lekin Actucal screen pe render karvana web me ReactDOM krta hai and mobile me bhi reactNative hota hai woh krta hai thats the reason we also need ReactDOM.


## Actual Job of REACT and ReactDOM-> so when we are creating the element with our custom react and consoling it woh ek element ki tarah show hora hai DOM element ki tarah but when we are creating the element with actual react woh console me buss ek object ki tarah aa raha hai jsime type,ref,props,store,owner,ref kuch keys values hai asa kyu. So let me tell you when we are creating an element with custom react woh js hee hai woh actual DOm element create kar raha hai but React Dom element nahi create karta it creates a blueprints that how should our element will look like ek blueprint create krta hai ki is element ki yeh proerty hogi yeh id hogi yeh class hogi yeh styles hogi yeh text content hoga yeh react create krta hai and then us blueprint ko ReactDOM ka render method as a input leta hai and actual DOm element create karta hai blueprint ko use krke and DOM me append krdeta hai given root mein.